metadata.name: DIANOS
metadata.description:
Creator of the vision universe the god of the gods  
 
Dianos is the creator of visible and hidden universe,witness of everything. He imagined through the darkness even before the known times and the first lines of The Vision legend was written. At the moment the first image reflected on Dianosâ€™s eye melt had its first spark after years and started ages which follow one another. by belief the cornea providing the bond between universe and dianos reflects everything that have ever happened and will happen. To write the ancient book Dianos collects them. The day sacred cornea loses its light is the day there will be nothing left to see in the Vision universe.
